      <title>以色列与哈马斯停火谈判处于转折点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-06/israel-asks-people-to-leave-rafah-banks-rush-to-saudi-arabia-the-future-of-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列与伊朗支持的激进组织哈马斯之间的停火谈判已进入迄今为止最关键的阶段。]]></description>
