    <item>
      <title>法官威胁特朗普因违反禁言令而入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[监督唐纳德·特朗普封口费审判的纽约法官表示，如果这位前总统继续违反旨在保护陪审员和证人安全的禁言令，他可能别无选择，只能入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/trump-found-in-contempt-a-second-time-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 13:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟表示准备使用所有贸易工具抵御中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/europe-says-ready-to-use-all-trade-tools-to-defend-against-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩在巴黎与习近平会谈后表示，如果中国未能提供公平的市场准入，欧盟准备动用一切可用工具来保卫其经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/europe-says-ready-to-use-all-trade-tools-to-defend-against-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 11:34:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京在新任期前夕下令进行战术核演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在他第五任期就职前一天，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京下令俄罗斯军队进行涉及战术核武器的作战演习，加剧了他与西方的对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-will-hold-tactical-nuclear-weapon-drills-tass-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 07:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
